Chisuvi (apex in English) zvinoreva pa[[chimiso]] panosangana mapango anobata denga remba yakavakwa ine madziro akaita denderedzwa. Denga iri kana richinge rapfirirwa kazhinji rinenge riiine kumbwa kwe[[charaka]]. 


Shoko rokuti chisuvi rinogona kushandiswawo kutsanangura pachimiso panosangana zviso zve[[dumba]] zvine kuumbwa kwe[[gonyanhatu]].
